(43921, 136988, 0, 1, 'Edges', '“The Edges” is a call for more authentic music in Macau and South East Asia. It is a response to the dominance of Cantopop and “mass-target, mass market” mass produced music found on the radio and television. The song looks to independent music, “The Edges”, to provide a voice for people who desire music which is more personal and more truthful. It praises people who support original music, “listen to the b-sides” and keep fighting for an artistic voice. It finishes by talking about the obstacles that artists have to overcome (“how many times we gonna kick the doors off / only to find another wall before us”) by looking to the future and finding strength as a community, “a thousand voices bring back the chorus”', '2012-02-29 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '', '', 229, '', 'Frontline Caste', 'Geoff Churchill@Frontline Caste', 'Simon Lok@Frontline Caste', 'Indie', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-02-29 11:33:15', '2015-03-12 13:50:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(43922, 90521, 3673, 4, 'Speechless DEMO', '就像時間一直經過\r\n身邊的人事物會不經意地改變消失\r\n卻也會以別種形式重新回到你身旁\r\n\r\n那麼，離別也不用太過悲傷了。\r\n因為不管我們到了什麼地方\r\n都不會忘記\r\n曾經', '2012-02-29 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 5, '那些關於誰的故事被寫下 結局又在哪\r\n現實理想 還在掙扎\r\n堅持下去或許是孤獨的逞強 真的理解嗎\r\n妥協變化 還是倔強\r\n\r\n而我們又會去什麼地方\r\n路上遇見了多少嚮往\r\n學會的 遺失了 \r\n不曾輕言放棄的深刻\r\n\r\n每次身體共同說不完的話 能夠帶走嗎\r\n裝進心臟 任他豢養\r\n就像看不見彼此的黑暗之中 卻明白光亮\r\n就在身旁 不曾迷惘\r\n\r\n而我們又會去什麼地方\r\n路上遇見了多少嚮往\r\n開心的 遺憾了\r\n相信誰帶著誰卻忘了', '', 240, '', '子安', '煎', '玫瑰花牛肉', '玫瑰花牛肉', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-02-29 12:05:48', '2015-03-12 13:50:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
